  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.06,
      "text": "Screen English"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.06,
      "end": 20.97,
      "text": "With Monsters with Monsters"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.97,
      "end": 23.59,
      "text": "영화 감상과 영어 공부를 동시에"
    },
    {
      "start": 23.59,
      "end": 25.13,
      "text": "Screen English Time"
    },
    {
      "start": 25.13,
      "end": 28.67,
      "text": "11월에 함께하고 있는 영화는 갈매기"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.67,
      "end": 29.59,
      "text": "The Seagull"
    },
    {
      "start": 29.59,
      "end": 32.19,
      "text": "입니다. 아, 크쌤 오셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.41,
      "end": 33.43,
      "text": "Hello, happy Monday."
    },
    {
      "start": 33.81,
      "end": 35.59,
      "text": "아하, 이정자님께서도"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.59,
      "end": 38.23,
      "text": "Hello, 크쌤 하셨습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 38.57,
      "end": 40.87,
      "text": "Oh, hello. Thank you. Good morning."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.17,
      "end": 44.65,
      "text": "이렇게 좋은 에너지와 함께 월요일 오늘 시작해보려고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.63,
      "end": 49.89,
      "text": "특히, it firstly seemed like a complicated love story, 그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.13,
      "end": 50.99,
      "text": "Very complicated."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.25,
      "end": 53.77,
      "text": "But actually, it helped us to explore"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.77,
      "end": 56.83,
      "text": "the complexities of human nature."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.83,
      "end": 60.29,
      "text": "Yes, human nature is complicated."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.93,
      "end": 62.83,
      "text": "굉장히 철학적으로 접근을 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.05,
      "end": 63.93,
      "text": "Just like love."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.03,
      "end": 64.29,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.73,
      "end": 65.11,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.11,
      "end": 68.39,
      "text": "특히 주인공들의 그 관계를 보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.39,
      "end": 71.11,
      "text": "Constantine하고 이리나"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.11,
      "end": 73.13,
      "text": "이 관계가 좀 특별하지 않나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.43,
      "end": 74.43,
      "text": "Very 특별해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.63,
      "end": 75.49,
      "text": "Very special."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.75,
      "end": 75.91,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.07,
      "end": 77.61,
      "text": "What is going on with them?"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.67,
      "end": 78.91,
      "text": "Who loves who?"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.91,
      "end": 81.37,
      "text": "과연 어떤 사랑일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.57,
      "end": 84.71,
      "text": "이 모자지간이 참 신기했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.71,
      "end": 85.15,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.35,
      "end": 86.93,
      "text": "So, I think they love each other"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.93,
      "end": 90.27,
      "text": "because they are mother and son after all."
    },
    {
      "start": 90.87,
      "end": 92.97,
      "text": "Mother and son, they should love each other."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.07,
      "end": 93.33,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.33,
      "end": 94.87,
      "text": "But the problem is"
    },
    {
      "start": 94.87,
      "end": 97.09,
      "text": "she seems to put her love for her work,"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.51,
      "end": 99.19,
      "text": "her fame, her career"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.19,
      "end": 101.93,
      "text": "above her love for her son."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.23,
      "end": 104.69,
      "text": "So, she needs to show more love for her son."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.77,
      "end": 105.27,
      "text": "맞습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.69,
      "end": 107.69,
      "text": "And he is, yeah, he's hurt."
    },
    {
      "start": 107.93,
      "end": 109.57,
      "text": "He's going through a difficult time."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.15,
      "end": 111.67,
      "text": "He's like a gloomy teenager."
    },
    {
      "start": 111.93,
      "end": 112.23,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 112.23,
      "end": 114.41,
      "text": "So, it's not easy."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.07,
      "end": 116.19,
      "text": "You know, like 중이."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.59,
      "end": 117.45,
      "text": "He's like a 중이."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.81,
      "end": 119.03,
      "text": "중이병이 있는 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.05,
      "end": 119.39,
      "text": "아, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.53,
      "end": 121.41,
      "text": "중이보다 한참 날 많은데."
    },
    {
      "start": 121.57,
      "end": 123.99,
      "text": "아, 철이 좀 덜 들었구나."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.13,
      "end": 124.65,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 124.95,
      "end": 125.95,
      "text": "He needs to find himself."
    },
    {
      "start": 126.07,
      "end": 126.91,
      "text": "Yeah, 맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 127.05,
      "end": 129.01,
      "text": "그리고 이 두 주인공뿐 아니라"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.01,
      "end": 131.47,
      "text": "다른 주인공들도 살펴보면"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.47,
      "end": 134.57,
      "text": "그 어긋난 사랑들을 하고 있잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.01,
      "end": 136.35,
      "text": "그러다 보니까 각자가 다"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.35,
      "end": 138.15,
      "text": "they bothered themselves."
    },
    {
      "start": 139.15,
      "end": 141.69,
      "text": "서로를 스스로 자악하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.69,
      "end": 143.67,
      "text": "그런 행태까지 보이고 있었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 143.79,
      "end": 146.13,
      "text": "Yeah, one of them is dying."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.37,
      "end": 146.39,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 146.65,
      "end": 148.35,
      "text": "One of them is just lost."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.65,
      "end": 150.03,
      "text": "I think they're all lost."
    },
    {
      "start": 150.25,
      "end": 151.37,
      "text": "They're all a little lost."
    },
    {
      "start": 151.39,
      "end": 151.79,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 152.11,
      "end": 153.43,
      "text": "So, I felt so bad for them."
    },
    {
      "start": 153.59,
      "end": 153.93,
      "text": "Did you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 153.93,
      "end": 156.63,
      "text": "Yeah, it's hard to like really root"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.63,
      "end": 158.79,
      "text": "for one single character in this movie."
    },
    {
      "start": 158.85,
      "end": 161.13,
      "text": "만약에 그래도 한 명을 응원해야 한다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.13,
      "end": 162.49,
      "text": "크쌤은 누굴 응원하시겠어요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 162.51,
      "end": 163.15,
      "text": "한 명만?"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.59,
      "end": 165.77,
      "text": "Well, there's no superhero and no bad guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 165.87,
      "end": 166.83,
      "text": "They're all crazy."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.01,
      "end": 167.15,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 167.41,
      "end": 169.27,
      "text": "So, it's difficult to choose just one."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.27,
      "end": 171.79,
      "text": "But, I'm going to have to choose Constantine."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.93,
      "end": 172.45,
      "text": "저도요."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.67,
      "end": 173.09,
      "text": "You too."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.15,
      "end": 173.43,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.63,
      "end": 174.59,
      "text": "He's an artist."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.75,
      "end": 178.11,
      "text": "아무래도 이게 주인공 중에 또 주인공이지 않습니까?"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.31,
      "end": 179.75,
      "text": "It's an artist이기도 하고."
    },
    {
      "start": 179.83,
      "end": 181.51,
      "text": "And I feel for him as a fellow man."
    },
    {
      "start": 181.61,
      "end": 181.85,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.21,
      "end": 183.67,
      "text": "I mean, the girl he likes"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.67,
      "end": 185.57,
      "text": "is running off with another guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 185.75,
      "end": 187.89,
      "text": "He wants to express himself."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.89,
      "end": 188.21,
      "text": "Right."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.21,
      "end": 190.51,
      "text": "And I just hope that he grows up well."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.65,
      "end": 191.21,
      "text": "Me too."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.21,
      "end": 194.05,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 먼저 듣고 올게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 194.05,
      "end": 196.05,
      "text": "Every summer I come down here"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.05,
      "end": 197.73,
      "text": "and I am insulted by you."
    },
    {
      "start": 197.83,
      "end": 199.83,
      "text": "Then you can find yourself another manager."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.07,
      "end": 200.19,
      "text": "Fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 200.43,
      "end": 202.37,
      "text": "I'm going into town and I'm not coming back."
    },
    {
      "start": 202.49,
      "end": 204.41,
      "text": "Farewell, my deepest apologies"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.41,
      "end": 207.13,
      "text": "for being unable to magically conjure horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.13,
      "end": 208.23,
      "text": "out of filet."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.94,
      "end": 210.5,
      "text": "How hard is it to find a horse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 211.52,
      "end": 214.94,
      "text": "It was another nervous moment."
    },
    {
      "start": 215.44,
      "end": 216.08,
      "text": "Calm down."
    },
    {
      "start": 216.22,
      "end": 217.4,
      "text": "아, 깜짝 놀랐어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 217.48,
      "end": 218.56,
      "text": "Relax, relax."
    },
    {
      "start": 218.76,
      "end": 220.22,
      "text": "Someone is very angry."
    },
    {
      "start": 220.22,
      "end": 224.46,
      "text": "자, 지금 이리나가 이 맨션의 주인이기는 했지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.46,
      "end": 227.64,
      "text": "she didn't know the farm situation well."
    },
    {
      "start": 227.92,
      "end": 229.46,
      "text": "Yeah, she wants to go into town."
    },
    {
      "start": 229.84,
      "end": 231.56,
      "text": "음내 가자, she says."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.7,
      "end": 232.28,
      "text": "All of a sudden."
    },
    {
      "start": 232.54,
      "end": 233.22,
      "text": "All of a sudden."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.46,
      "end": 236.08,
      "text": "After a picnic, after some alcohol,"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.56,
      "end": 237.48,
      "text": "let's go into town."
    },
    {
      "start": 237.48,
      "end": 239.98,
      "text": "But the horses are doing farm work"
    },
    {
      "start": 239.98,
      "end": 243.6,
      "text": "and she needs the horses to pull her carriage into town."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.92,
      "end": 246.12,
      "text": "And her manager explains this,"
    },
    {
      "start": 246.3,
      "end": 247.88,
      "text": "but she's not so happy."
    },
    {
      "start": 247.88,
      "end": 250.24,
      "text": "And then he gets really, really angry."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.34,
      "end": 250.56,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.74,
      "end": 254.12,
      "text": "서로 의견이 받아들여지지가 않는 장면이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.72,
      "end": 257.18,
      "text": "I think the manager just said what he had to say."
    },
    {
      "start": 258.12,
      "end": 261.12,
      "text": "그냥 자기가 해야 할 말을 했을 뿐인데."
    },
    {
      "start": 261.34,
      "end": 262.22,
      "text": "But he exploded."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.52,
      "end": 263.06,
      "text": "아, 그쵸."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.08,
      "end": 264.14,
      "text": "He was not just talking."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.4,
      "end": 266.22,
      "text": "말이 안 통하니까 화가 났나봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 266.26,
      "end": 268.1,
      "text": "He was screaming at the top of his lungs."
    },
    {
      "start": 268.1,
      "end": 271.38,
      "text": "I think he's dealt a lot with her"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.38,
      "end": 273.98,
      "text": "and he's sick and tired of her."
    },
    {
      "start": 274.36,
      "end": 275.68,
      "text": "So he resigns."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.78,
      "end": 277.24,
      "text": "I think he wants to resign."
    },
    {
      "start": 277.46,
      "end": 279.1,
      "text": "And this is a good excuse to resign."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.1,
      "end": 279.36,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 279.52,
      "end": 281.0,
      "text": "갑자기 그래서 화가 나니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.0,
      "end": 283.02,
      "text": "나중에 그만둬버리겠어요 라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 283.02,
      "end": 284.64,
      "text": "외치게 되는 것까지 있었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.64,
      "end": 285.5,
      "text": "And he runs away."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.8,
      "end": 286.26,
      "text": "Bye-bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 286.26,
      "end": 287.78,
      "text": "저는 걱정이 됐던 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.78,
      "end": 291.32,
      "text": "The manager's wife must have had a hard time"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.32,
      "end": 292.92,
      "text": "between these two people."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.0,
      "end": 293.4,
      "text": "Oh, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 293.58,
      "end": 295.94,
      "text": "My husband's gonna lose his job."
    },
    {
      "start": 296.44,
      "end": 297.76,
      "text": "We're gonna get kicked out of the house."
    },
    {
      "start": 297.86,
      "end": 299.5,
      "text": "정말 당황스러웠을 것 같습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 300.28,
      "end": 302.08,
      "text": "그럼 주요 표현들 점검을 해볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.84,
      "end": 304.04,
      "text": "Insulted by"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.04,
      "end": 305.94,
      "text": "Insulted by"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.94,
      "end": 309.14,
      "text": "I-N-S-U-L-T-E-D"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.14,
      "end": 309.82,
      "text": "by"
    },
    {
      "start": 316.26,
      "end": 318.56,
      "text": "Insulted by"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.56,
      "end": 320.49,
      "text": "모욕 당하는"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.49,
      "end": 322.55,
      "text": "Conjure horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.55,
      "end": 324.63,
      "text": "Conjure horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.63,
      "end": 325.63,
      "text": "라고 들으셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.79,
      "end": 326.35,
      "text": "Conjure"
    },
    {
      "start": 326.35,
      "end": 328.29,
      "text": "It sounds very French."
    },
    {
      "start": 328.31,
      "end": 328.71,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 329.27,
      "end": 331.65,
      "text": "그래서 약간 주문을 외워서"
    },
    {
      "start": 331.65,
      "end": 334.55,
      "text": "뭔가가 뿅 하고 나타나게 하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.55,
      "end": 335.57,
      "text": "라는 동사입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 335.79,
      "end": 337.21,
      "text": "Yeah, think of a magic show."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.29,
      "end": 337.61,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 337.93,
      "end": 339.15,
      "text": "You know that they have a blanket"
    },
    {
      "start": 339.15,
      "end": 341.99,
      "text": "and they take the blanket off their hands"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.99,
      "end": 343.89,
      "text": "and all of a sudden they have pigeons."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.01,
      "end": 344.29,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 344.29,
      "end": 346.51,
      "text": "꼭 비둘기들이 날라다니더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 346.85,
      "end": 347.27,
      "text": "Ta-da!"
    },
    {
      "start": 347.39,
      "end": 347.65,
      "text": "Ta-da!"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.11,
      "end": 349.39,
      "text": "I conjured pigeons."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.67,
      "end": 350.43,
      "text": "그럴 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 350.43,
      "end": 351.23,
      "text": "이 Conjure"
    },
    {
      "start": 351.23,
      "end": 353.19,
      "text": "이라는 동사를 활용하실 수가 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.85,
      "end": 354.33,
      "text": "이번에는"
    },
    {
      "start": 354.33,
      "end": 355.35,
      "text": "Conjure horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 355.35,
      "end": 356.19,
      "text": "라고 했으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.19,
      "end": 356.99,
      "text": "아하"
    },
    {
      "start": 356.99,
      "end": 357.59,
      "text": "말을"
    },
    {
      "start": 357.59,
      "end": 358.39,
      "text": "짜잔"
    },
    {
      "start": 358.39,
      "end": 359.59,
      "text": "하고 주문처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 359.59,
      "end": 360.69,
      "text": "이렇게 magic처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 360.69,
      "end": 361.71,
      "text": "나타나게 하다"
    },
    {
      "start": 361.71,
      "end": 362.39,
      "text": "라는 동사"
    },
    {
      "start": 362.39,
      "end": 363.25,
      "text": "구가 되겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.43,
      "end": 363.57,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.69,
      "end": 365.05,
      "text": "Out of thin air"
    },
    {
      "start": 365.05,
      "end": 366.93,
      "text": "이런 표현이랑 많이 같이 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.05,
      "end": 369.17,
      "text": "아 아주 환상적인 조합이네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 369.69,
      "end": 370.75,
      "text": "Out of thin air"
    },
    {
      "start": 370.75,
      "end": 371.53,
      "text": "이라고 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 371.53,
      "end": 372.39,
      "text": "난데없이"
    },
    {
      "start": 372.39,
      "end": 373.37,
      "text": "라고 해석이 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.37,
      "end": 374.75,
      "text": "Out of thin air"
    },
    {
      "start": 374.75,
      "end": 375.29,
      "text": "Ta-da!"
    },
    {
      "start": 375.67,
      "end": 376.57,
      "text": "Thin air"
    },
    {
      "start": 376.57,
      "end": 377.37,
      "text": "아셨죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 377.65,
      "end": 378.97,
      "text": "자 다시 한번 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 379.77,
      "end": 381.37,
      "text": "Every summer I come down here"
    },
    {
      "start": 381.37,
      "end": 383.03,
      "text": "and I am insulted by you."
    },
    {
      "start": 383.15,
      "end": 384.47,
      "text": "Then you can find yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 384.47,
      "end": 385.15,
      "text": "another manager."
    },
    {
      "start": 385.39,
      "end": 385.49,
      "text": "Fine!"
    },
    {
      "start": 385.73,
      "end": 386.67,
      "text": "I'm going into town"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.67,
      "end": 387.69,
      "text": "and I'm not coming back."
    },
    {
      "start": 387.81,
      "end": 388.37,
      "text": "Farewell"
    },
    {
      "start": 388.37,
      "end": 389.75,
      "text": "my deepest apologies"
    },
    {
      "start": 389.75,
      "end": 390.91,
      "text": "for being unable"
    },
    {
      "start": 390.91,
      "end": 392.49,
      "text": "to magically conjure horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 392.49,
      "end": 393.73,
      "text": "out of thin air!"
    },
    {
      "start": 394.28,
      "end": 395.04,
      "text": "How hard is it"
    },
    {
      "start": 395.04,
      "end": 395.84,
      "text": "to find a horse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.16,
      "end": 398.96,
      "text": "서로가"
    },
    {
      "start": 398.96,
      "end": 399.82,
      "text": "didn't want to hear"
    },
    {
      "start": 399.82,
      "end": 401.1,
      "text": "what the other said."
    },
    {
      "start": 401.46,
      "end": 401.64,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.0,
      "end": 402.54,
      "text": "와"
    },
    {
      "start": 402.54,
      "end": 403.4,
      "text": "막무가내"
    },
    {
      "start": 403.4,
      "end": 404.68,
      "text": "현장이었습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 404.84,
      "end": 405.62,
      "text": "Is it the weather?"
    },
    {
      "start": 405.86,
      "end": 406.88,
      "text": "It's really hot."
    },
    {
      "start": 407.04,
      "end": 407.34,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 407.48,
      "end": 408.44,
      "text": "Everybody's sweating."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.86,
      "end": 409.44,
      "text": "엎친 데"
    },
    {
      "start": 409.44,
      "end": 410.44,
      "text": "덮친 격"
    },
    {
      "start": 410.44,
      "end": 411.12,
      "text": "과 같았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.34,
      "end": 411.7,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.82,
      "end": 412.66,
      "text": "What a disaster."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.66,
      "end": 414.08,
      "text": "자 이리나가"
    },
    {
      "start": 414.08,
      "end": 415.02,
      "text": "먼저 이야기를 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 415.84,
      "end": 416.48,
      "text": "Every summer"
    },
    {
      "start": 416.48,
      "end": 417.7,
      "text": "I come down here"
    },
    {
      "start": 417.7,
      "end": 419.36,
      "text": "and I am insulted"
    },
    {
      "start": 419.36,
      "end": 420.26,
      "text": "by you."
    },
    {
      "start": 420.26,
      "end": 421.58,
      "text": "Every summer"
    },
    {
      "start": 421.58,
      "end": 423.64,
      "text": "매 여름마다"
    },
    {
      "start": 423.64,
      "end": 425.12,
      "text": "I come down here"
    },
    {
      "start": 425.12,
      "end": 426.32,
      "text": "내가 여기 내려오면"
    },
    {
      "start": 426.32,
      "end": 428.1,
      "text": "and I am insulted"
    },
    {
      "start": 428.1,
      "end": 429.16,
      "text": "by you"
    },
    {
      "start": 429.16,
      "end": 430.24,
      "text": "당신에게"
    },
    {
      "start": 430.24,
      "end": 432.51,
      "text": "모욕을 당해."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.51,
      "end": 434.43,
      "text": "Then you can find yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 434.43,
      "end": 435.69,
      "text": "another manager."
    },
    {
      "start": 435.69,
      "end": 437.45,
      "text": "네 이 매니저이"
    },
    {
      "start": 437.45,
      "end": 438.53,
      "text": "뭐라고 이야기했냐면"
    },
    {
      "start": 438.53,
      "end": 439.41,
      "text": "그럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 439.41,
      "end": 441.27,
      "text": "you can find yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 441.27,
      "end": 442.27,
      "text": "another manager."
    },
    {
      "start": 442.69,
      "end": 443.61,
      "text": "다른 지배인을"
    },
    {
      "start": 443.61,
      "end": 444.83,
      "text": "좀 찾아보시죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 445.27,
      "end": 445.55,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 445.81,
      "end": 446.79,
      "text": "So is this her manager"
    },
    {
      "start": 446.79,
      "end": 447.65,
      "text": "for work?"
    },
    {
      "start": 447.81,
      "end": 449.15,
      "text": "Because she's an actress?"
    },
    {
      "start": 449.33,
      "end": 450.97,
      "text": "I think he may take care"
    },
    {
      "start": 450.97,
      "end": 452.43,
      "text": "of all of her affairs."
    },
    {
      "start": 452.65,
      "end": 453.21,
      "text": "Maybe."
    },
    {
      "start": 453.91,
      "end": 455.03,
      "text": "I thought at first"
    },
    {
      "start": 455.03,
      "end": 456.21,
      "text": "he was like a butler."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.21,
      "end": 457.61,
      "text": "You know like a"
    },
    {
      "start": 457.61,
      "end": 458.53,
      "text": "집사"
    },
    {
      "start": 458.53,
      "end": 459.61,
      "text": "같은 느낌."
    },
    {
      "start": 460.01,
      "end": 460.53,
      "text": "But maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 460.53,
      "end": 461.77,
      "text": "he takes care of"
    },
    {
      "start": 461.77,
      "end": 462.79,
      "text": "everything for her."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.13,
      "end": 464.21,
      "text": "너무 부담스러웠을"
    },
    {
      "start": 464.21,
      "end": 464.97,
      "text": "것 같긴 하네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.97,
      "end": 465.49,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.69,
      "end": 466.89,
      "text": "I would not want that job."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.35,
      "end": 468.75,
      "text": "Fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.11,
      "end": 470.65,
      "text": "I'm going into town"
    },
    {
      "start": 470.65,
      "end": 472.53,
      "text": "and I'm not coming back."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.63,
      "end": 472.75,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 473.13,
      "end": 474.11,
      "text": "다른 지배인을"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.11,
      "end": 474.77,
      "text": "찾아보세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.77,
      "end": 475.65,
      "text": "라고 외친"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.65,
      "end": 476.07,
      "text": "그"
    },
    {
      "start": 476.07,
      "end": 477.37,
      "text": "매니저들의"
    },
    {
      "start": 477.37,
      "end": 478.95,
      "text": "이야기에 이어서"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.95,
      "end": 479.69,
      "text": "Fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 479.97,
      "end": 480.31,
      "text": "좋아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.63,
      "end": 481.43,
      "text": "라고 이야기하면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 481.43,
      "end": 482.99,
      "text": "I'm going into town."
    },
    {
      "start": 483.31,
      "end": 484.19,
      "text": "나는 마을에 가서"
    },
    {
      "start": 484.19,
      "end": 485.67,
      "text": "and I'm not coming back."
    },
    {
      "start": 485.97,
      "end": 486.87,
      "text": "돌아오지 않겠어"
    },
    {
      "start": 486.87,
      "end": 487.79,
      "text": "라고 외칩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.95,
      "end": 488.61,
      "text": "Are you going to walk?"
    },
    {
      "start": 489.57,
      "end": 491.57,
      "text": "How are you going to get into town?"
    },
    {
      "start": 491.59,
      "end": 492.93,
      "text": "그게 방법이 없을 텐데"
    },
    {
      "start": 492.93,
      "end": 495.14,
      "text": "Farewell."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.14,
      "end": 495.44,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 495.52,
      "end": 496.3,
      "text": "그러니까 매니저가"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.3,
      "end": 497.08,
      "text": "Farewell"
    },
    {
      "start": 497.08,
      "end": 497.68,
      "text": "이라고 합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 497.88,
      "end": 499.18,
      "text": "이거 작별 인사가 되겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 499.3,
      "end": 499.92,
      "text": "Bye bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 500.06,
      "end": 501.0,
      "text": "안녕히 가세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.48,
      "end": 501.66,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.78,
      "end": 503.3,
      "text": "Farewell is like a very formal"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.3,
      "end": 504.64,
      "text": "way to say bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 504.76,
      "end": 506.34,
      "text": "And you usually say it"
    },
    {
      "start": 506.34,
      "end": 507.24,
      "text": "when you're angry"
    },
    {
      "start": 507.24,
      "end": 509.08,
      "text": "out of sarcasm"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.08,
      "end": 509.14,
      "text": "nowadays."
    },
    {
      "start": 509.14,
      "end": 509.82,
      "text": "아 약간"
    },
    {
      "start": 509.82,
      "end": 511.52,
      "text": "비꼬면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 511.52,
      "end": 513.4,
      "text": "특히 화난 상황에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 513.4,
      "end": 514.32,
      "text": "이렇게 Farewell"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.32,
      "end": 514.64,
      "text": "이라고"
    },
    {
      "start": 514.64,
      "end": 516.4,
      "text": "좀 부정적인 상황에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.4,
      "end": 516.84,
      "text": "쓰이는"
    },
    {
      "start": 516.84,
      "end": 518.06,
      "text": "작별 인사가 되겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.32,
      "end": 518.62,
      "text": "Fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.72,
      "end": 519.16,
      "text": "Farewell."
    },
    {
      "start": 519.32,
      "end": 520.02,
      "text": "Bye bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 520.02,
      "end": 521.92,
      "text": "My deepest apologies"
    },
    {
      "start": 521.92,
      "end": 523.42,
      "text": "for being unable"
    },
    {
      "start": 523.42,
      "end": 525.06,
      "text": "to magically conjure"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.06,
      "end": 525.74,
      "text": "horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 525.74,
      "end": 527.48,
      "text": "out of thin air."
    },
    {
      "start": 527.48,
      "end": 529.16,
      "text": "자 이거 해석이"
    },
    {
      "start": 529.16,
      "end": 529.92,
      "text": "잘 되셨나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 530.32,
      "end": 532.18,
      "text": "My deepest apologies"
    },
    {
      "start": 532.18,
      "end": 534.14,
      "text": "for being unable"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.14,
      "end": 536.76,
      "text": "to magically conjure"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.76,
      "end": 537.64,
      "text": "horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 537.64,
      "end": 539.32,
      "text": "out of thin air."
    },
    {
      "start": 540.08,
      "end": 540.86,
      "text": "난데없이"
    },
    {
      "start": 540.86,
      "end": 542.06,
      "text": "말들을"
    },
    {
      "start": 542.06,
      "end": 543.36,
      "text": "정말 마법처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 543.36,
      "end": 544.28,
      "text": "뿅 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 544.28,
      "end": 546.86,
      "text": "불쑥 대령하지 못한 것이"
    },
    {
      "start": 546.86,
      "end": 549.0,
      "text": "엄청 죄송하네요"
    },
    {
      "start": 549.0,
      "end": 550.54,
      "text": "라고 해석을 하시면 돼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.66,
      "end": 552.08,
      "text": "Is this a sincere apology?"
    },
    {
      "start": 552.32,
      "end": 552.68,
      "text": "아니요."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.72,
      "end": 553.82,
      "text": "He was very sarcastic."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.08,
      "end": 554.42,
      "text": "Very."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.82,
      "end": 556.14,
      "text": "My deepest apologies."
    },
    {
      "start": 556.56,
      "end": 557.92,
      "text": "It already sounds sarcastic."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.98,
      "end": 558.26,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.26,
      "end": 559.36,
      "text": "처음부터 아주"
    },
    {
      "start": 559.36,
      "end": 560.26,
      "text": "비꼬는 말투였죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 561.6,
      "end": 562.58,
      "text": "How hard is it"
    },
    {
      "start": 562.58,
      "end": 563.64,
      "text": "to find a horse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 563.78,
      "end": 564.68,
      "text": "How hard is it"
    },
    {
      "start": 564.68,
      "end": 565.56,
      "text": "to find a horse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 565.74,
      "end": 566.42,
      "text": "이리나가"
    },
    {
      "start": 566.42,
      "end": 567.44,
      "text": "재차 질문합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 567.9,
      "end": 568.66,
      "text": "아니 도대체"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.66,
      "end": 569.44,
      "text": "말 찾는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 569.44,
      "end": 570.36,
      "text": "그렇게 어렵나?"
    },
    {
      "start": 570.62,
      "end": 571.62,
      "text": "라고 이야기합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.26,
      "end": 573.76,
      "text": "이 문장을 들어보면요."
    },
    {
      "start": 573.8,
      "end": 574.84,
      "text": "She looks so innocent"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.84,
      "end": 575.74,
      "text": "on the other hand."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.9,
      "end": 576.4,
      "text": "Oh really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 576.54,
      "end": 576.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 576.96,
      "end": 578.18,
      "text": "아무것도 몰라요."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.26,
      "end": 578.88,
      "text": "이런 상황 아니에요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.2,
      "end": 579.7,
      "text": "Well maybe"
    },
    {
      "start": 579.7,
      "end": 581.08,
      "text": "너무 귀하게 자라가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 581.08,
      "end": 582.18,
      "text": "너무 귀하게 자라서"
    },
    {
      "start": 582.18,
      "end": 583.22,
      "text": "She's an actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.42,
      "end": 584.3,
      "text": "She doesn't know"
    },
    {
      "start": 584.3,
      "end": 585.14,
      "text": "about farm work."
    },
    {
      "start": 585.22,
      "end": 586.54,
      "text": "The horses are working"
    },
    {
      "start": 586.54,
      "end": 587.16,
      "text": "on the farm."
    },
    {
      "start": 587.64,
      "end": 588.76,
      "text": "She has no idea."
    },
    {
      "start": 588.94,
      "end": 589.42,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.52,
      "end": 590.28,
      "text": "She's clueless."
    },
    {
      "start": 591.2,
      "end": 591.72,
      "text": "자 이 장면"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.72,
      "end": 592.56,
      "text": "한 번 더 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 593.3,
      "end": 594.9,
      "text": "Every summer I come down here"
    },
    {
      "start": 594.9,
      "end": 596.54,
      "text": "and I am insulted by you."
    },
    {
      "start": 596.66,
      "end": 597.98,
      "text": "Then you can find yourself"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.98,
      "end": 598.68,
      "text": "another manager."
    },
    {
      "start": 598.9,
      "end": 599.04,
      "text": "Fine."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.26,
      "end": 600.2,
      "text": "I'm going into town"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.2,
      "end": 601.2,
      "text": "and I'm not coming back."
    },
    {
      "start": 601.34,
      "end": 601.9,
      "text": "Farewell."
    },
    {
      "start": 602.14,
      "end": 603.24,
      "text": "My deepest apologies"
    },
    {
      "start": 603.24,
      "end": 604.42,
      "text": "for being unable"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.42,
      "end": 605.98,
      "text": "to magically conjure horses"
    },
    {
      "start": 605.98,
      "end": 607.06,
      "text": "and a philess."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.06,
      "end": 608.55,
      "text": "How hard is it"
    },
    {
      "start": 608.55,
      "end": 609.35,
      "text": "to find a horse?"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.41,
      "end": 612.41,
      "text": "강연희님께서요."
    },
    {
      "start": 612.79,
      "end": 614.41,
      "text": "전 사실 이 영화가"
    },
    {
      "start": 614.41,
      "end": 615.93,
      "text": "조금 어렵더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.43,
      "end": 618.41,
      "text": "솔직히 제 스타일은 아니었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 618.67,
      "end": 621.05,
      "text": "그래도 다양한 작품을 접하는 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.05,
      "end": 622.59,
      "text": "영어 공부에 도움이 되겠죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 623.07,
      "end": 624.87,
      "text": "크쌤도 한국 영화 보면서"
    },
    {
      "start": 624.87,
      "end": 626.81,
      "text": "한국어 공부하셨는지 궁금해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 627.27,
      "end": 629.71,
      "text": "어떤 영화가 제일 좋았는지도요."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.71,
      "end": 632.23,
      "text": "Oh, that's a good question."
    },
    {
      "start": 632.75,
      "end": 634.09,
      "text": "I've seen many, many movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 634.59,
      "end": 635.63,
      "text": "Korean movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.79,
      "end": 636.51,
      "text": "Korean movies."
    },
    {
      "start": 636.99,
      "end": 638.03,
      "text": "Before I came to Korea,"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.13,
      "end": 639.67,
      "text": "I watched about three"
    },
    {
      "start": 639.67,
      "end": 641.29,
      "text": "classic Korean movies"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.29,
      "end": 642.65,
      "text": "to learn about Korea."
    },
    {
      "start": 643.15,
      "end": 643.71,
      "text": "뭐였을까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.87,
      "end": 644.77,
      "text": "One of them was"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.77,
      "end": 645.67,
      "text": "The Classic."
    },
    {
      "start": 646.33,
      "end": 647.33,
      "text": "The Classic."
    },
    {
      "start": 647.53,
      "end": 648.49,
      "text": "It's a classic movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 648.49,
      "end": 650.25,
      "text": "about love."
    },
    {
      "start": 650.37,
      "end": 651.53,
      "text": "The other was"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.53,
      "end": 652.13,
      "text": "what was it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 652.13,
      "end": 653.05,
      "text": "태극기 휘날리며"
    },
    {
      "start": 653.05,
      "end": 654.39,
      "text": "That was good."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.85,
      "end": 655.87,
      "text": "It was like"
    },
    {
      "start": 655.87,
      "end": 656.79,
      "text": "a Korean version"
    },
    {
      "start": 656.79,
      "end": 658.21,
      "text": "of Saving Private Ryan."
    },
    {
      "start": 658.31,
      "end": 658.71,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 659.17,
      "end": 659.79,
      "text": "전쟁 영화."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.43,
      "end": 661.01,
      "text": "And then"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.01,
      "end": 661.83,
      "text": "the one with"
    },
    {
      "start": 661.83,
      "end": 662.49,
      "text": "전지연."
    },
    {
      "start": 662.75,
      "end": 663.47,
      "text": "엽기적인 그녀."
    },
    {
      "start": 663.55,
      "end": 665.03,
      "text": "아우, 재밌는 영화들."
    },
    {
      "start": 665.05,
      "end": 665.77,
      "text": "그거 반했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.01,
      "end": 666.67,
      "text": "아, 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.81,
      "end": 667.45,
      "text": "한국에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 667.45,
      "end": 668.29,
      "text": "더 좋은 인상을"
    },
    {
      "start": 668.29,
      "end": 669.45,
      "text": "갖고 오실 수가"
    },
    {
      "start": 669.45,
      "end": 670.21,
      "text": "있었겠네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 670.37,
      "end": 670.49,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 670.79,
      "end": 671.45,
      "text": "네, 좋았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 671.61,
      "end": 672.51,
      "text": "세 개 다."
    },
    {
      "start": 672.69,
      "end": 673.65,
      "text": "아, 그렇군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.85,
      "end": 674.43,
      "text": "아무튼"
    },
    {
      "start": 674.43,
      "end": 675.71,
      "text": "강연희님"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.71,
      "end": 676.97,
      "text": "내 마음에"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.97,
      "end": 678.65,
      "text": "쏙 들지는 않더라도"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.65,
      "end": 679.37,
      "text": "항상 이렇게"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.37,
      "end": 680.33,
      "text": "열린 마음으로"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.33,
      "end": 681.21,
      "text": "들어주시면"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.21,
      "end": 681.75,
      "text": "여러모로"
    },
    {
      "start": 681.75,
      "end": 683.03,
      "text": "많이 도움이 되실 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 683.23,
      "end": 684.17,
      "text": "I feel you too."
    },
    {
      "start": 684.33,
      "end": 685.75,
      "text": "내 스타일도 아니었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 685.85,
      "end": 686.15,
      "text": "솔직히."
    },
    {
      "start": 686.79,
      "end": 688.79,
      "text": "너무 솔직한"
    },
    {
      "start": 688.79,
      "end": 689.91,
      "text": "우리 크쌤이셨어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 690.47,
      "end": 691.35,
      "text": "우리 내일 또"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.35,
      "end": 692.39,
      "text": "만나도록 하겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 692.65,
      "end": 693.05,
      "text": "See you tomorrow."
    }
  ]
}